#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:4
msgid "fg - bring job to foreground"
msgstr "fg - 將工作帶到前景"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:7
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "概要"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:9
msgid "fg [PID]"
msgstr "fg [PID]"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:14
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:16
msgid ""
"The **fg** builtin brings the specified :ref:`job <syntax-job-control>` to "
"the foreground, resuming it if it is stopped. While a foreground job is "
"executed, fish is suspended. If no job is specified, the last job to be used "
"is put in the foreground. If ``PID`` is specified, the job containing a "
"process with the specified process ID is put in the foreground."
msgstr ""
"**fg** 內建命令會將指定的\\ :ref:`工作 <syntax-job-control>`\\ 帶到前景，如果"
"該工作已停止則會恢復執行。當前景工作執行時，fish 會暫停。若未指定任何工作，則"
"會將最後使用的工作置於前景。若指定了 ``PID``，則會將包含指定進程 ID 的進程所"
"屬的工作帶到前景。"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:21
msgid ""
"For compatibility with other shells, job expansion syntax is supported for "
"``fg``. A *PID* of the format **%1** will foreground job 1. Job numbers can "
"be seen in the output of :doc:`jobs <jobs>`."
msgstr ""
"為了與其他外殼相容，``fg`` 支援工作展開語法。格式為 **%1** 的 PID 會將工作 1 "
"帶到前景。工作編號可在 :doc:`jobs <jobs>` 命令的輸出中查看。"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:24
msgid "The **--help** or **-h** option displays help about using this command."
msgstr "**--help** 或 **-h** 選項會顯示關於此命令的幫助資訊。"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:27
msgid "Example"
msgstr "範例"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:29
msgid "``fg`` will put the last job in the foreground."
msgstr "``fg`` 會將最後一個工作放到前景執行。"

#: ../../../cmds/fg.rst:31
msgid "``fg %3`` will put job 3 into the foreground."
msgstr "``fg %3`` 會將工作 3 放到前景執行。"
